               <msContents>
                  <summary>Maṣḥafa gǝnzat “Book of the Funeral Ritual”
 I) Maṣḥafa gǝnzat “Book
                     of the Funeral Ritual” (fols. 4ra-154ra)
 - Introduction (fols.
                     4ra-10va)
 - Discourse of St Athanasius on death (fols. 10va-17va)
 -
                     Maṣḥaf za-wäḍʾat ʾǝm-ʾIyarusalem “Book that Came from Jerusalem” (fols.
                     17va-25ra)
 - Homily by St Jacob of Serug for the funeral of priests and
                     deacons (fols. 77va-92va)
 - Homily by ʾabbā Salāmā, Metropolitan of
                     Ethiopia (fols. 96vb-99ra)
 - Lǝfāfa ṣǝdq “Bandlet of Righteousness” (fols.
                     103va-106rb)
 - Mangada samāy “Journey to Heaven” (fols.
                     106rb-108rb).</summary>
